\id 2TH NT0014 Tsikimba (kdl) (Auna Kambari) 2010 
\h 2 Tasaloniya 
\toc1 Ukanikorongi u Ire Ubana a Asu u Aza a Tasaloniya 
\toc2 2 Tasaloniya 
\toc3 2 Tas. 
\mt2 Ukanikorongi u Ire Ubana a Asu u 
\mt1 Aza a Tasaloniya 
\is1 Ukukpa̱ u kadyanshi 
\ip Atoni a ɗa aꞌa̱ri a Tasaloniya a ɗa Bulus wa koronku ukanikorongi u na vi. Ukanikorongi u ire u ɗa yi la vi ubana a asu u Atoni a ɗa aꞌa̱ri a kuden ku pige ka ka̱ri a ikengi i kushiva̱. U korongu ta̱ u ɗa kpaci aza roku pini ɗe a ka wenishike ta̱ uwenishike u kaɓan a kaci ka ugono u Yesu. Aza roku a le a da aꞌa̱ ta̱ n ukanikorongi u ɗa u wuta̱i ara Bulus, shegai kaɓan ka. 
\ip A ukanikorongi u na vi, Bulus wenishike ta̱ ukuna u mayun a kaci ka kain ka Yesu wa gono. I doku ta̱ a ili iꞌya wa̱ri u korongi a ukuna u na vi. Ili i tatsu iꞌya pini iꞌya iꞌa̱ri n kalen iꞌya Bulus korongi pini a ukanikorongi u na vi. U tonuko le ta̱ ukuna u ugono u Yesu. U tonuko le an upana u ikyamba u ɗa a ka so vi mavura ma a asu u Kashila̱ wa. Upana u ikyamba u na vi wa kotso ta̱, kpam kain ka uwunvuga ka pini. A makorishi, u da a ma̱tsa̱ manyan hal n a vani ugono u Yesu. 
\ip Gba̱ ili i na yi gogo‑na i woko tsu ta̱ i mayun, tyoku ɗa iꞌa̱ri i mayun a asu u aza a Tasaloniya a aꞌayin a ɗa Bulus korongi ukanikorongi u na vi. 
\is1 Ili iꞌya iꞌa̱ri a tagara̱da u na vi 
\io1 Idyani (1:1-2) 
\io1 Ugono u Asheku wa tuko ta̱ ukuna u mayun (1:3-12) 
\io1 Kotsu Asheku a gono wa (2:1-12) 
\io1 Rongoi n upityanangu (2:13-17) 
\io1 Yanyi kavasu n i yanyi manyan (3:1-15) 
\io1 Kavasu ka makorishi (3:16-18) 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 A̱tsu an Bulus n Sila n Timoti a̱tsa tsa korongu ukanikorongi u na vi ubana a asu u Atoni a Tasaloniya aza ɗa aꞌa̱ri ama a Kashila̱ Tata u tsunu, kpam aꞌa̱ri a asuvu a Asheku Yesu Kirisiti Kawauwi. 
\p  
\v 2 Kavasu ka va̱ ka Kashila̱ Tata n Asheku Yesu Kawauwi a na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ ukuna u shinga na̱ ndishi n shinga! 
\s1 Kavasu ka ucikpa 
\p  
\v 3 Ama a va̱, u gan ta̱ an kain dem tsu tsu cikpa Kashila̱ adama a ɗe. Tsu tsu cikpa ta̱ an upityanangu u ɗe wa̱ri a ugbonguro maco kpam ya dem a asuvu a ɗe wa̱ ta̱ a udoku uciga utoku.  
\v 4 Ɗa i zuwai tsa yan baci kadyanshi ka ɗe a asu u Atoni a roku, tsu tsu yan ta̱ maza̱nga̱ an iꞌa̱ri n akawunki kpam i shamgbai pini n upityanangu ko an ya pana ikyamba n mavura cika. 
\p  
\v 5 Upana u ikyamba u nala vi, u wenike ta̱ an Kashila̱ ka yanka ya dem afada dere. Adama a nala Kashila̱ ka kece ɗa̱ ta̱ a asuvu a ama a shinga a ɗa a ka uwa a tsugono tsu Kashila̱, kpam eɗa na a ka yan mavura adama a tsugono tsu nala tsi.  
\v 6 Kashila̱ ka tsu yan ta̱ ili dere. Wa yan ta̱ aza ɗa a ka tukuso ɗa̱ upana u ikyamba vi mavura.  
\v 7 Wa tuko ɗa̱ ta̱ kpam uwunvuga a asuvu a upana u ikyamba vi hal n a̱tsu dem. Ukuna u na wa gita̱ ta̱ aꞌayin a ɗa Yesu Asheku u wuta̱i a zuba u tuwa̱i n atsumate a zuba a ucira a ne, kpam n aletsu a akina.\fig Utuwa̱ u Asheku n atsumate a zuba|src="2 Thessalonians_1_7-8.tif" size="span" loc="2Thessalonians 1:7" ref="2 Tas. 1:7" \fig* 
\p  
\v 8 Asheku a tsunu Yesu wa yan ta̱ aza ɗa bawu a revei Kashila̱ kpam a ꞌyuwain upana̱ka Kadyanshi ka Shinga ka Yesu Asheku mavura.  
\v 9 A ka zuwa le ta̱ a upana u ikyamba; wata, ukpa̱ u ɗa bawu wa̱ri n utyoku. A ka pece le ta̱ n Asheku kpam a asuvu a tsupige tsu ucira tsu ne bawu utyoku.  
\v 10 Ukuna u na wa gita̱ ta̱ aꞌayin a ɗa Asheku a ka gono u wushi icikpali n tsupige a asu u aza ɗa aꞌa̱ri n upityanangu ara ne kpam aꞌa̱ri ama a ne. Eɗa̱ iꞌa̱ ta̱ pini a asuvu a le, kpaci i wushuku ta̱ n iꞌya tsu danai. 
\p  
\v 11 Ukuna u na u ɗa u zuwa tsu tsa lya kelime n uyan kavasu, tsa̱ra̱ u zuwa ɗa̱ i woko ama a ɗa aꞌa̱ri dere tyoku ɗa wa ciga. Tsa yan ta̱ kpam kavasu, ucira u Kashila̱ u ɓa̱nga̱ ɗa̱ i yain gba̱ ikuna i shinga iꞌya ya ciga i yain. Upityanangu u ɗe u ɗa u zuwa ɗa̱ uciga u uyan ukuna u nala vi.  
\v 12 Nala wa zuwa ya dem u na̱ka̱ kala ka Asheku a tsunu Yesu tsupige adama a ɗe. Kpam a ka na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ ta̱ tsupige tsi hal n eyi dem. Kashila̱ ka tsunu ka ka yan ukuna u nala vi a asu u Asheku Yesu Kawauwi, adama a ukuna u shinga u le. 
\c 2  
\s1 Magono ma Uꞌya̱nga̱sa̱ka̱ 
\p  
\v 1 Ama a va̱, tsa tonuko ɗa̱ ta̱ tyoku ɗa Asheku a tsunu Yesu Kawauwi wa tuwa̱ n tyoku ɗa a ka ɓolomgbono tsu a asu u te tsa̱ra̱ tsu gawunsa n eyi.  
\v 2 Kotsu vu laza kute vu dambula a kaci ka aza ɗa a tsu ciga a dana kain ka Asheku ka rawa ɗe wa. Gaawan a ka ciga ta̱ a dana a pana̱ka tsu ta̱ an tsa dansa akani a Kashila̱, ko a kadyanshi ka uza roku u danai ko kpam ka a korongi.  
\v 3 Kotsu i a̱sa̱ka̱ le a yanka ɗa̱ ugboji n udani u le wa. 
\p Ukuna u maci vi u ɗa, kain ki ka tuwa̱ wa, she a ꞌya̱nga̱sa̱ka̱ Kashila̱ cika kpam Magono ma Uꞌya̱nga̱sa̱ka̱ ma nala mi ma wenike kaci ka ne, aku a wacinsa yi.  
\v 4 Wa gonuko ta̱ kaci ka ne uzapige, aku u bidya kaci ka ne u la ta̱ kameli, ko kpam ili iꞌya a ka lyaka kayala. Hal gba̱m u tsu uwa ta̱ a Kuwa ku Kashila̱, n u dansi karara aya Kashila̱. 
\p  
\v 5 Ciɓai aꞌayin a ɗa ma̱ri kaɓolo n a̱ɗa̱ n tsu yanka ɗa̱ ta̱ alabari a ili i na yi.  
\v 6 Gogo‑na i reve la vi ɗe ili iꞌya ya shamkpa yi, kpaci a asuvu a aꞌayin a ne a ɗa koshi a ka wenike yi.  
\v 7 Ucira u cingi u ɗa wa yan tsilala n Kashila̱ u ɗa pini wa yan manyan usokongi, shegai uza ɗa wa ka̱ngu u ɗa vi wa lya ta̱ kelime n uka̱ngu u ɗa hal she kain ka a ka takpa yi.  
\v 8 Pini nala, ɗa Magono ma Uꞌya̱nga̱sa̱ka̱ mi ma wenike kaci ka ne, aya uza ɗa Yesu Asheku wa wuna n uwule u una̱ u ne. Wa wacinsa yi ta̱ kpam n tsupige tsu utuwa̱ u ne. 
\p  
\v 9 Magono ma Uꞌya̱nga̱sa̱ka̱ mi ma tuwa̱ ta̱ ma yain manyan ma Kanangasi\f + \fr 2:9 \ft Kanangasi; wata, “Shetan” kala ka dem ka Kala̱pa̱nsi.\f* a asu u ucira u kaɓan n iryoci i kaɓan, n ikunesavu iꞌya iꞌa̱ri i kaɓan.  
\v 10 Kpam wa yanka ta̱ gba̱ ili i cingi kau‑kau manyan tsa̱ra̱ u yinsa̱ ama ɗa a ka wacinsa. Wacinsa ɗa a ka wacinsa le kpaci a ꞌyuwan ta̱ uciga ili iꞌya iꞌa̱ri i maci, a ꞌyuwan la vi ɗe iwauwi iꞌya i wuta̱i a asu u Kashila̱.  
\v 11 Adama a nala, Kashila̱ ka sukunku le ta̱ ili i ucira iꞌya ya yinsa̱ le i zuwa le a wushuku n kaɓan ki.  
\v 12 Nala a ka kiɗa̱ga le ugana kpaci a ka pana ta̱ kayanyan ka ili i cingi iꞌya a ka yansa, a una̱ u ɗa a ka wushuku n ukuna u mayun. 
\s1 Shamgbai n ucira 
\p  
\v 13 Ama a va̱, u gan ta̱ an kain dem tsu tsu cikpa Kashila̱ adama a ɗe. Asheku a ka ciga ɗa̱ ta̱, kpam u ɗanga̱sa ɗa̱ ta̱ tun caupa a kagita̱ wa wauwa ɗa̱ ta̱. Iwauwi i tuwa̱ ta̱ an Kulu Keri ku zuwa ɗa̱ i wokoi sarara, i tuwa̱ ta̱ kpam an i wushuki n kadyanshi ka ukuna u mayun.  
\v 14 U isa̱ ɗa̱ ta̱ utuwa̱ a iwauwi an tsu tonuko ɗa̱ ukuna u Kadyanshi ka Shinga, tsa̱ra̱ i tsa̱ra̱ agadu a asuvu a tsupige tsu Asheku a tsunu Yesu Kawauwi. 
\p  
\v 15 Ama a va̱, adama a ukuna u na vi, u ka̱na̱ ta̱ i shamgba n ucira, i ka̱na̱ uwenishike u ɗa tsu wenishike ɗa̱ a asu u kadyanshi n ikorongi. 
\p  
\v 16 Kashila̱ Tata u tsunu wa ciga tsu ta̱. Adama a iyali i na yi ɗa u gbamatangu tsu asuvu kpam u ɗa bawu wa̱ri n utyoku n uzuwuka u uma u pige.  
\v 17 Tsu yanka ɗa̱ ta̱ kavasu tsa̱ra̱ Yesu Kawauwi Asheku n Kashila̱ Tata u tsunu u zuwa atakasuvu a ɗe a rongo n ucira, tsu yan ta̱ kpam kavasu tsa̱ra̱ a na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ ucira u uyan u ili i shinga n kadyanshi ka shinga. 
\c 3  
\s1 Yanka tsu kavasu 
\p  
\v 1 A makorishi, ama a va̱, n folo ɗa̱ ta̱ i yanka tsu kavasu, i gita̱ i yain kavasu tsa̱ra̱ akani a Asheku a tambura gogo kpam a na̱ka̱ a ɗa tsupige a asu u ɗa baci dem a rawai, tyoku ɗa i yain aꞌayin a ɗa akani yi a rawai ara ɗe.  
\v 2 I yain kpam kavasu a wauwa tsu a akere a aza a cingi, kpaci ya dem ɗa u wushuki n Asheku wa.  
\v 3 Shegai Asheku aꞌa̱ ta̱ n ushamkpa u kazuwamgbani, wa zuwa ɗa̱ ta̱ i gbama kpam u kirana n a̱ɗa̱ a asu u uza u cingi.  
\v 4 Tsa̱ ta̱ n uzuwa u uma a asu u Asheku ya yansa ta̱ iꞌya tsu tonuko ɗa̱ i yansa, tsa̱ ta̱ kpam n u uzuwa u uma ya lya ta̱ kapala n uyan iꞌya.  
\v 5 A̱sa̱ka̱ Yesu Kawauwi Asheku u wenike ɗa̱ tyoku ɗa Kashila̱ ka ciga ɗa̱. U wenike ɗa̱ kpam akawunki a upana u ikyamba tyoku ɗa eyi u kawunki. 
\s1 Kotsu i woko awonvoli wa 
\p  
\v 6 Gogo‑na ama a va̱, na̱ka̱ ɗa tsu na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ udani u na a asuvu a kala ka Asheku a tsunu Yesu Kawauwi. Banai dan n uza ɗa wa̱ri kawonvoli a asuvu a ɗe uza ɗa bawu wa rongo tyoku u uwenishike u ɗa i wushai ara tsunu.  
\v 7 Eɗa̱ n kaci ka ɗe i reve ta̱ u ka̱na̱i i toni tyoku ɗa a̱tsu tsa̱ri. Aꞌayin a ɗa tsa̱ri kaɓolo n a̱ɗa̱, tsu yan uwonvoli wa.  
\v 8 Tsu tsu lya ilikulya i uza bawu tsu tsupai iꞌya wa. Tsu tsu ma̱tsa̱ ta̱ tsu yain manyan kaara n kayin adama a ɗa kotsu tsu woko kala̱nda̱m a asu u uza wa.  
\v 9 Yan ɗa tsu yain nala ko an u wokoi tsa̱ri n ucira u ɗa tsa fuɗa tsu dana i lyatangu tsu. Shegai tsu yan nala wa kpaci tsa ciga ta̱ tsu woko ɗa̱ iryoci iꞌya ya tono.  
\v 10 Aꞌayin a ɗa tsa̱ri n a̱ɗa̱, tsu na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ ta̱ ili iꞌya ya tono: “Uza ɗa baci gai u ꞌyuwain uyan manyan, kotsu a na̱ka̱ yi ilikulya wa.” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsu reve ta̱ aza roku a ɗe dusuku ɗa a dusuki ndishi n gbani bawu a ka yan ili la, hal a ka̱ngi manyan ma aza roku.  
\v 12 Adama a nala a asuvu a kala ka Asheku a tsunu Yesu Kawauwi, tsa folo ta̱ ama a na yi, tsa ɓarana le ta̱ gba̱m a a̱sa̱ka̱ kugengu a ꞌya̱nga̱ a gita̱ manyan a boluko kaci ka le ilikulya. 
\p  
\v 13 Ama a va̱, kotsu i wowo n uyan ili iꞌya iꞌa̱ri mai wa. 
\p  
\v 14 Aza ɗa a ꞌyuwain upana ili iꞌya tsu danai a ukanikorongi u na vi, i tonuko ama a kirana n ele. Banai dan i a̱sa̱ka̱ le tsa̱ra̱ a woko n uwono.  
\v 15 Kotsu i bidya ama a na yi tyoku u atokulalu a ɗe wa, shegai i dansa n ele tyoku u utoku u ɗe u ɗa wa̱ri a kuwa ku ɗe, uza ɗa ya ɓarana u yan baci ukuna u cingi. 
\s1 Idyani i makorishi 
\p  
\v 16 A̱sa̱ka̱ Asheku a ndishi n shinga a na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ ndishi n shinga kain dem ko niɗa baci ukuna wa woko. Asheku a rongo n a̱ɗa̱ gba̱. 
\p  
\v 17 Gogo‑na idyani i va̱ iꞌya na, n kukere ku va̱ ka ma korongu iꞌya. Mpa Bulus, n tsu yan ta̱ ili i na a makorishi ma ukanikorongi u ɗa baci dem n korongi, kpam i tsu wenike ta̱ an ara va̱ ɗa u wuta̱i mayun.\fig Bulus wa yan ikorongi|src="2 Thessalonians_3_17-ok.tif" size="span" loc="2Thessalonians 3:17" ref="2 Tas. 3:17" \fig* 
\p  
\v 18 A̱sa̱ka̱ ukuna u shinga u Asheku a tsunu Yesu Kawauwi u rongo n a̱ɗa̱ gba̱ ɗe. 